              <a id="btn-3965421299" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3965421299">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1377398/">藠头与秋葵</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3965421299">2023-10-24 21:04:42</a>
          <span class="comment-location">北京</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">毛姆自诩为二流作家恐怕是客观的，文字不考究、叙事略笨拙，但好在总有股感人的力量，刀锋其实是类似《悉达多》的故事内核，想想《月亮和六便士》好像也差不多</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/2035162/?comment_id=3965421299"></div>
    </div>
